---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Syntax & Synapse">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">About Syntax & Synapse</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
      <p class="text-xl mb-6">
        Welcome to <strong>Syntax & Synapse</strong>, where code meets cognition. This blog explores the rapidly evolving intersection of artificial intelligence and software development.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        We believe that understanding AI is becoming as fundamental as understanding algorithms. Our goal is to bridge the gap between cutting-edge AI research and practical software development, making complex concepts accessible to developers at all levels.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>AI Development</strong>: Practical implementations of machine learning models, LLMs, and AI agents</li>
        <li><strong>Software Engineering</strong>: Modern development practices optimized for AI applications</li>
        <li><strong>Research Insights</strong>: Distilled analysis of the latest AI research papers</li>
        <li><strong>Real-world Applications</strong>: Case studies and production deployment strategies</li>
        <li><strong>Tooling & Best Practices</strong>: MLOps, testing strategies, and development workflows</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
      <p>
        This blog is built with modern web technologies to demonstrate best practices:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Astro.js</strong> for fast, static site generation</li>
        <li><strong>Tailwind CSS v4</strong> for responsive, utility-first styling</li>
        <li><strong>GitHub Pages</strong> for reliable, free hosting</li>
        <li><strong>Markdown</strong> for content management with Astro Content Collections</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Connect</h2>
      <p>
        Built and maintained by a developer passionate about the future of AI and software. This blog represents our journey exploring how these fields continue to converge and transform each other.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-base-100 border border-base-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Get in Touch</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-base-600">
          Have questions or suggestions for topics? Reach out through GitHub or follow along as we explore the future of AI-powered development.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>